'''Si-shae-ral''' was an [[Eickarie]] tribe. Many of their [[Noble/Legends|nobles]] and elders were taken prisoner by the [[The Warlord|Warlord]] in order to keep the tribe and its allies subservient to him, though they would be freed by the [[501st Legion/Legends|501st Legion]] and their [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Ha-ran]] in the [[Capture of the Warlord|Battle of Kariek]], where many would aide in the capture of the Warlord.

